cmos filter

this time i want to build filters with the cmos cd 4069.

this time i want to build filters with the cmos cd 4069.

low pass filter¶

lets get started with the simplest filter, a low pass filter.

Capacitor C2

for this filter we expect the cutoff frequency to be:

$$ \begin{array}{c} f = \frac{1}{2 \pi RC} = \frac{1}{2 \pi 100k * 100n} = 159Hz \end{array} $$

to [C,l=$C_1$] (1,3) {}

to [short,-o] (-3.5,0) {}
(-3.5,0) node[left] {IN}


(0.75,0) to [C,l=$C_2$] (3,0)
(3,0) to [R,l=$R_load$] (3,-2) {}
to (3,-2) node [ground] {}
